summary: The new visuals for packaging and promotions will feature a “pea-sized” amount of toothpaste for children under six years.

headline: Oil prices slip lower, consolidating ahead of Fed rate decision
summary: Investing.com -- Oil prices slipped lower Wednesday, consolidating after recent strong gains on heightened concerns over disruptions in Russian production, with focus now squarely on the conclusion of a U.S. Federal Reserve policy meeting.
